headline: Palantir Technologies Announces Two-Day Pop-Up Experience in Seoul
summary: DENVER, September 28, 2025--Palantir Technologies will open a two-day pop-up merchandise store in Seoul's culturally dynamic Seongdong-gu district from October 14-15, marking the company's first dedicated retail experience for its passionate Korean fanbase. The temporary store at 26 Achasan-ro 11ga-gil in Seongdong-gu will showcase six items—five being sold publicly for the first time. Merchandise will be available in limited quantities on a first-come, first-served basis.
